 libmeshaware
--------------

libmeshaware is an Ada library for writing "mesh aware" applications.

 1. Supported routing protocols
 2. License


1. Supported routing protocols

Initially libmeshaware only supports the 'B.A.T.M.A.N. advanced' routing protocol. [1]


